track_notes: There are others path to reach this summit, this one is the normal way that you could join to cime du Diable or Pointe des 3 communes; the panorama is wonderfull and it is a good place for Radio.
this is an easy walk, you can park at the guards house

This track is not ok in winter when there is snow.
You can park at the entrance of the nationnal Parc du Mercantour (guard house). Plenty room on summit but no trees for antenna setup! The place is fine with a wonderfull landscape.

To reach the parking, you must drive 6km on a forest road. Not many places to park! The walk to the summit is easy even if some part are very sloop. if you go down following the crest, you must not suffer vertigo, and have a GPS to show you the way down.
